OL,3,CRhona's fish finger sandwiches raise
OL,4,C#55,000 for charity
OL,6,FA Jersey cafe is celebrating two
OL,7,Fdecades of feeding hungry beachgoers
OL,8,Fand raising funds for charity through
OL,9,Fa popular menu item.
OL,11,FRhonas' at the Beach in Gorey is known
OL,12,Ffor its fish finger sandwiches and
OL,13,Fdonates all proceeds to local good
OL,14,Fcauses.
OL,16,FOwner Rhona Hewitt says that over the
OL,17,Fpast seven years, they have managed to
OL,18,Fraise over #55,000.
