OL,3,CRhona's fish finger sandwiches raise
OL,4,C#55,000 for charity
OL,6,FShe adds that the idea came from
OL,7,Fhosting coffee mornings for Macmillan
OL,8,FCancer Support.
OL,10,F"I just thought 'this is fab!'," Rhona
OL,11,Fexplains.
OL,13,F"We would go, eat cake and donate
OL,14,Fmoney and I thought that was something
OL,15,FI could do at the cafe.
OL,17,F"Because it was so successful, I
OL,18,Fthought I'd carry it on in a different
OL,19,Fform."
