OL,3,CRhona's fish finger sandwiches raise
OL,4,C#55,000 for charity
OL,6,FDespite complications with her own
OL,7,Fhealth this year, Rhona says she
OL,8,Fremains committed to doing all she can
OL,9,Fto keep fundraising.
OL,11,FOn Friday (8 August), this year's
OL,12,Fchosen charity - Enable Jersey - threw
OL,13,FRhona a beach party to celebrate the
OL,14,Fdonation milestone and the cafe's 20th
OL,15,Fbirthday.
OL,17,FThe organisation works to limit
OL,18,Fbarriers faced by islanders with
OL,19,Fdisabilities and campaigns for changes
OL,20,Fthat bring greater inclusivity.
