OL,6,FBeachability wheelchairs allowed
OL,7,Feveryone to take part in the evening
OL,8,Fof swimming, beach games and
OL,9,Fcompetitions.
OL,11,FDanielle Self, Enable's Fundraising
OL,12,Fand Awareness Coordinator, says the
OL,13,Fcharity could not operate without
OL,14,FRhona's ongoing support.
OL,16,F"She's our biggest donor every single
OL,17,Fmonth which makes a huge difference to
OL,18,Fus," Danielle explains.
