OL,3,CRhona's fish finger sandwiches raise
OL,4,C#55,000 for charity
OL,6,F"We're a small charity, we rely solely
OL,7,Fon donations, so having that every
OL,8,Fmonth just gives us a huge boost to be
OL,9,Fable to help people in Jersey with
OL,10,Fdisabilities."
OL,12,FWhilst the fish finger sandwiches face
OL,13,Fa battle against bacon rolls to be the
OL,14,Fcafe's best seller, Rhona says she
OL,15,Fnever dreamed the campaign would be so
OL,16,Fsuccessful.
OL,18,F"People literally come down just for a
OL,19,Ffish finger sandwich because they know
OL,20,Fit does good," Rhona explains. "It's
OL,21,Famazing."
