OL,6,FAs for the next 20 years, Rhona adds
OL,7,Fshe will keep supporting local good
OL,8,Fcauses.
OL,10,F"The community at Gorey is absolutely
OL,11,Ffabulous," she says.
OL,13,F"Whatever we do, we're supporting
OL,14,Fcharities along the way because that's
OL,15,Fa really important part of Rhonas."
